55#define ISC_MD_md5 ISC_MD_MD5
56#define ISC_MD_sha1 ISC_MD_SHA1
57#define ISC_MD_sha224 ISC_MD_SHA224
58#define ISC_MD_sha256 ISC_MD_SHA256
59#define ISC_MD_sha384 ISC_MD_SHA384
60#define ISC_MD_sha512 ISC_MD_SHA512

62#define hmac_register_algorithm(alg) \
63 static isc_result_t \
64 hmac##alg##_createctx(dst_key_t *key, \
65 dst_context_t *dctx) { \
66 return (hmac_createctx(ISC_MD_##alg, key, dctx)); \
67 } \
68 static void \
69 hmac##alg##_destroyctx(dst_context_t *dctx) { \
70 hmac_destroyctx(dctx); \
71 } \
72 static isc_result_t \
73 hmac##alg##_adddata(dst_context_t *dctx, \
74 const isc_region_t *data) { \
75 return (hmac_adddata(dctx, data)); \
76 } \
77 static isc_result_t \
78 hmac##alg##_sign(dst_context_t *dctx, \
79 isc_buffer_t *sig) { \
80 return (hmac_sign(dctx, sig)); \
81 } \
82 static isc_result_t \
83 hmac##alg##_verify(dst_context_t *dctx, \
84 const isc_region_t *sig) { \
85 return (hmac_verify(dctx, sig)); \
86 } \
87 static bool \
88 hmac##alg##_compare(const dst_key_t *key1, \
89 const dst_key_t *key2) { \
90 return (hmac_compare(ISC_MD_##alg, key1, key2)); \
91 } \
92 static isc_result_t \
93 hmac##alg##_generate(dst_key_t *key, \
94 int pseudorandom_ok, \
95 void (*callback)(int)) { \
96 UNUSED(pseudorandom_ok); \
97 UNUSED(callback); \
98 return (hmac_generate(ISC_MD_##alg, key)); \
99 } \
100 static bool \
101 hmac##alg##_isprivate(const dst_key_t *key) { \
102 return (hmac_isprivate(key)); \
103 } \
104 static void \
105 hmac##alg##_destroy(dst_key_t *key) { \
106 hmac_destroy(key); \
107 } \
108 static isc_result_t \
109 hmac##alg##_todns(const dst_key_t *key, isc_buffer_t *data) { \
110 return (hmac_todns(key, data)); \
111 } \
112 static isc_result_t \
113 hmac##alg##_fromdns(dst_key_t *key, isc_buffer_t *data) { \
114 return (hmac_fromdns(ISC_MD_##alg, key, data)); \
115 } \
116 static isc_result_t \
117 hmac##alg##_tofile(const dst_key_t *key, const char *directory) { \
118 return (hmac_tofile(ISC_MD_##alg, key, directory)); \
119 } \
120 static isc_result_t \
121 hmac##alg##_parse(dst_key_t *key, isc_lex_t *lexer, \
122 dst_key_t *pub) { \
123 return(hmac_parse(ISC_MD_##alg, key, lexer, pub)); \
124 } \
125 static dst_func_t hmac##alg##_functions = { \
126 hmac##alg##_createctx, \
127 NULL, /*%< createctx2 */ \
128 hmac##alg##_destroyctx, \
129 hmac##alg##_adddata, \
130 hmac##alg##_sign, \
131 hmac##alg##_verify, \
132 NULL, /*%< verify2 */ \
133 NULL, /*%< computesecret */ \
134 hmac##alg##_compare, \
135 NULL, /*%< paramcompare */ \
136 hmac##alg##_generate, \
137 hmac##alg##_isprivate, \
138 hmac##alg##_destroy, \
139 hmac##alg##_todns, \
140 hmac##alg##_fromdns, \
141 hmac##alg##_tofile, \
142 hmac##alg##_parse, \
143 NULL, /*%< cleanup */ \
144 NULL, /*%< fromlabel */ \
145 NULL, /*%< dump */ \
146 NULL, /*%< restore */ \
147 }; \
148 isc_result_t \
149 dst__hmac##alg##_init(dst_func_t **funcp) { \
150 REQUIRE(funcp != NULL); \
151 if (*funcp == NULL) { \
152 *funcp = &hmac##alg##_functions; \
153 } \
154 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS); \
155 }
156
157static isc_result_t
158hmac_fromdns(isc_md_type_t type, dst_key_t *key, isc_buffer_t *data);
159
160struct dst_hmac_key {
161 uint8_t key[ISC_MAX_BLOCK_SIZE];
162};
163
164static inline isc_result_t
165getkeybits(dst_key_t *key, struct dst_private_element *element) {
166 uint16_t *bits = (uint16_t *)element->data;
167
168 if (element->length != 2) {
169 return (DST_R_INVALIDPRIVATEKEY);
170 }
171
172 key->key_bits = ntohs(*bits);
173
174 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
175}
176
177static inline isc_result_t
178hmac_createctx(isc_md_type_t type, const dst_key_t *key,
179 dst_context_t *dctx)
180{
181 isc_result_t result;
182 const dst_hmac_key_t *hkey = key->keydata.hmac_key;
183 isc_hmac_t *ctx = isc_hmac_new(); /* Either returns or abort()s */
184
185 result = isc_hmac_init(ctx, hkey->key,
186 isc_md_type_get_block_size(type), type);
187 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
188 return (DST_R_UNSUPPORTEDALG);
189 }
190
191 dctx->ctxdata.hmac_ctx = ctx;
192 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
193}
194
195static inline void
196hmac_destroyctx(dst_context_t *dctx) {
197 isc_hmac_t *ctx = dctx->ctxdata.hmac_ctx;
198 REQUIRE(ctx != NULL);
199
200 isc_hmac_free(ctx);
201 dctx->ctxdata.hmac_ctx = NULL;
202}
203
204static inline isc_result_t
205hmac_adddata(const dst_context_t *dctx, const isc_region_t *data) {
206 isc_result_t result;
207 isc_hmac_t *ctx = dctx->ctxdata.hmac_ctx;
208
209 REQUIRE(ctx != NULL);
210
211 result = isc_hmac_update(ctx, data->base, data->length);
212 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
213 return (DST_R_OPENSSLFAILURE);
214 }
215
216 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
217}
218
219static inline isc_result_t
220hmac_sign(const dst_context_t *dctx, isc_buffer_t *sig) {
221 isc_hmac_t *ctx = dctx->ctxdata.hmac_ctx;
222 REQUIRE(ctx != NULL);
223 unsigned int digestlen;
224 unsigned char digest[ISC_MAX_MD_SIZE];
225
226 if (isc_hmac_final(ctx, digest, &digestlen) != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
227 return (DST_R_OPENSSLFAILURE);
228 }
229
230 if (isc_hmac_reset(ctx) != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
231 return (DST_R_OPENSSLFAILURE);
232 }
233
234 if (isc_buffer_availablelength(sig) < digestlen) {
235 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
236 }
237
238 isc_buffer_putmem(sig, digest, digestlen);
239
240 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
241}
242
243static inline isc_result_t
244hmac_verify(const dst_context_t *dctx, const isc_region_t *sig) {
245 isc_hmac_t *ctx = dctx->ctxdata.hmac_ctx;
246 unsigned int digestlen;
247 unsigned char digest[ISC_MAX_MD_SIZE];
248
249 REQUIRE(ctx != NULL);
250
251 if (isc_hmac_final(ctx, digest, &digestlen) != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
252 return (DST_R_OPENSSLFAILURE);
253 }
254
255 if (isc_hmac_reset(ctx) != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
256 return (DST_R_OPENSSLFAILURE);
257 }
258
259 if (sig->length > digestlen) {
260 return (DST_R_VERIFYFAILURE);
261 }
262
263 return (isc_safe_memequal(digest, sig->base, sig->length) ?
264 ISC_R_SUCCESS :
265 DST_R_VERIFYFAILURE);
266}
267
268static inline bool
269hmac_compare(isc_md_type_t type, const dst_key_t *key1, const dst_key_t *key2) {
270 dst_hmac_key_t *hkey1, *hkey2;
271
272 hkey1 = key1->keydata.hmac_key;
273 hkey2 = key2->keydata.hmac_key;
274
275 if (hkey1 == NULL && hkey2 == NULL) {
276 return (true);
277 } else if (hkey1 == NULL || hkey2 == NULL) {
278 return (false);
279 }
280
281 return (isc_safe_memequal(hkey1->key, hkey2->key,
282 isc_md_type_get_block_size(type)));
283}
284
285static inline isc_result_t
286hmac_generate(isc_md_type_t type, dst_key_t *key) {
287 isc_buffer_t b;
288 isc_result_t ret;
289 unsigned int bytes, len;
290 unsigned char data[ISC_MAX_MD_SIZE] = { 0 };
291
292 len = isc_md_type_get_block_size(type);
293
294 bytes = (key->key_size + 7) / 8;
295
296 if (bytes > len) {
297 bytes = len;
298 key->key_size = len * 8;
299 }
300
301 isc_nonce_buf(data, bytes);
302
303 isc_buffer_init(&b, data, bytes);
304 isc_buffer_add(&b, bytes);
305
306 ret = hmac_fromdns(type, key, &b);
307
308 isc_safe_memwipe(data, sizeof(data));
309
310 return (ret);
311}
312
313static inline bool
314hmac_isprivate(const dst_key_t *key) {
315 UNUSED(key);
316 return (true);
317}
318
319static inline void
320hmac_destroy(dst_key_t *key) {
321 dst_hmac_key_t *hkey = key->keydata.hmac_key;
322 isc_safe_memwipe(hkey, sizeof(*hkey));
323 isc_mem_put(key->mctx, hkey, sizeof(*hkey));
324 key->keydata.hmac_key = NULL;
325}
326
327static inline isc_result_t
328hmac_todns(const dst_key_t *key, isc_buffer_t *data) {
329 dst_hmac_key_t *hkey = key->keydata.hmac_key;
330 unsigned int bytes;
331
332 REQUIRE(hkey != NULL);
333
334 bytes = (key->key_size + 7) / 8;
335 if (isc_buffer_availablelength(data) < bytes) {
336 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
337 }
338 isc_buffer_putmem(data, hkey->key, bytes);
339
340 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
341}
342
343static inline isc_result_t
344hmac_fromdns(isc_md_type_t type, dst_key_t *key, isc_buffer_t *data) {
345 dst_hmac_key_t *hkey;
346 unsigned int keylen;
347 isc_region_t r;
348
349 isc_buffer_remainingregion(data, &r);
350 if (r.length == 0) {
351 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
352 }
353
354 hkey = isc_mem_get(key->mctx, sizeof(dst_hmac_key_t));
355 if (hkey == NULL) {
356 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
357 }
358
359 memset(hkey->key, 0, sizeof(hkey->key));
360
361 /* Hash the key if the key is longer then chosen MD block size */
362 if (r.length > (unsigned int)isc_md_type_get_block_size(type)) {
363 if (isc_md(type, r.base, r.length, hkey->key, &keylen)
364 != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
365 isc_mem_put(key->mctx, hkey, sizeof(dst_hmac_key_t));
366 return (DST_R_OPENSSLFAILURE);
367 }
368 } else {
369 memmove(hkey->key, r.base, r.length);
370 keylen = r.length;
371 }
372
373 key->key_size = keylen * 8;
374 key->keydata.hmac_key = hkey;
375
376 isc_buffer_forward(data, r.length);
377
378 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
379}

381static inline int
382hmac__get_tag_key(isc_md_type_t type) {
383 if (type == ISC_MD_MD5) {
384 return (TAG_HMACMD5_KEY);
385 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA1) {
386 return (TAG_HMACSHA1_KEY);
387 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA224) {
388 return (TAG_HMACSHA224_KEY);
389 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA256) {
390 return (TAG_HMACSHA256_KEY);
391 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA384) {
392 return (TAG_HMACSHA384_KEY);
393 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA512) {
394 return (TAG_HMACSHA512_KEY);
395 } else {
396 INSIST(0);
397 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
398 }
399}
400
401static inline int
402hmac__get_tag_bits(isc_md_type_t type) {
403 if (type == ISC_MD_MD5) {
404 return (TAG_HMACMD5_BITS);
405 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA1) {
406 return (TAG_HMACSHA1_BITS);
407 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA224) {
408 return (TAG_HMACSHA224_BITS);
409 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA256) {
410 return (TAG_HMACSHA256_BITS);
411 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA384) {
412 return (TAG_HMACSHA384_BITS);
413 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA512) {
414 return (TAG_HMACSHA512_BITS);
415 } else {
416 INSIST(0);
417 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
418 }
419}

421static inline isc_result_t
422hmac_tofile(isc_md_type_t type, const dst_key_t *key, const char *directory) {
423 dst_hmac_key_t *hkey;
424 dst_private_t priv;
425 int bytes = (key->key_size + 7) / 8;
426 uint16_t bits;
427
428 if (key->keydata.hmac_key == NULL) {
429 return (DST_R_NULLKEY);
430 }
431
432 if (key->external) {
433 return (DST_R_EXTERNALKEY);
434 }
435
436 hkey = key->keydata.hmac_key;
437
438 priv.elements[0].tag = hmac__get_tag_key(type);
439 priv.elements[0].length = bytes;
440 priv.elements[0].data = hkey->key;
441
442 bits = htons(key->key_bits);
443
444 priv.elements[1].tag = hmac__get_tag_bits(type);
445 priv.elements[1].length = sizeof(bits);
446 priv.elements[1].data = (uint8_t *)&bits;
447
448 priv.nelements = 2;
449
450 return (dst__privstruct_writefile(key, &priv, directory));
451}
452
453static inline int
454hmac__to_dst_alg(isc_md_type_t type) {
455 if (type == ISC_MD_MD5) {
456 return (DST_ALG_HMACMD5);
457 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA1) {
458 return (DST_ALG_HMACSHA1);
459 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA224) {
460 return (DST_ALG_HMACSHA224);
461 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA256) {
462 return (DST_ALG_HMACSHA256);
463 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA384) {
464 return (DST_ALG_HMACSHA384);
465 } else if (type == ISC_MD_SHA512) {
466 return (DST_ALG_HMACSHA512);
467 } else {
468 INSIST(0);
469 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
470 }
471}
472
473static inline isc_result_t
474hmac_parse(isc_md_type_t type, dst_key_t *key,
475 isc_lex_t *lexer, dst_key_t *pub)
476{
477 dst_private_t priv;
478 isc_result_t result, tresult;
479 isc_buffer_t b;
480 isc_mem_t *mctx = key->mctx;
481 unsigned int i;
482
483 UNUSED(pub);
484 /* read private key file */
485 result = dst__privstruct_parse(key, hmac__to_dst_alg(type), lexer, mctx,
486 &priv);
487 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
488 return (result);
489 }
490
491 if (key->external) {
492 result = DST_R_EXTERNALKEY;
493 }
494
495 key->key_bits = 0;
496 for (i = 0; i < priv.nelements && result == ISC_R_SUCCESS; i++) {
497 switch (priv.elements[i].tag) {
498 case TAG_HMACMD5_KEY:
499 case TAG_HMACSHA1_KEY:
500 case TAG_HMACSHA224_KEY:
501 case TAG_HMACSHA256_KEY:
502 case TAG_HMACSHA384_KEY:
503 case TAG_HMACSHA512_KEY:
504 isc_buffer_init(&b, priv.elements[i].data,
505 priv.elements[i].length);
506 isc_buffer_add(&b, priv.elements[i].length);
507 tresult = hmac_fromdns(type, key, &b);
508 if (tresult != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
509 result = tresult;
510 }
511 break;
512 case TAG_HMACMD5_BITS:
513 case TAG_HMACSHA1_BITS:
514 case TAG_HMACSHA224_BITS:
515 case TAG_HMACSHA256_BITS:
516 case TAG_HMACSHA384_BITS:
517 case TAG_HMACSHA512_BITS:
518 tresult = getkeybits(key, &priv.elements[i]);
519 if (tresult != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
520 result = tresult;
521 }
522 break;
523 default:
524 result = DST_R_INVALIDPRIVATEKEY;
525 break;
526 }
527 }
528 dst__privstruct_free(&priv, mctx);
529 isc_safe_memwipe(&priv, sizeof(priv));
530 return (result);
531}

534hmac_register_algorithm(sha1);
535hmac_register_algorithm(sha224);
536hmac_register_algorithm(sha256);
537hmac_register_algorithm(sha384);
538hmac_register_algorithm(sha512);
